    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2017-11-03</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2018-03-01T21:34:32Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Monitoring and Obtaining Needed Information to Track Opioids Responsibly Act of 2017 or the MONITOR Act of 2017</strong></p> <p>This bill amends the 21st Century Cures Act to require that in order for a state to receive&nbsp;funds to address the opioid abuse crisis&nbsp;the state's prescription drug monitoring program must meet specified requirements, including reporting within one business day when controlled substances are dispensed.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
