      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To ensure that the prescription drug monitoring program of each State receiving funds through the Account for the State Response to the Opioid Abuse Crisis meets certain minimum requirements, and for other purposes.</title>
